The exact extent of the surrounding areas is not clearly defined, but during the {{ill|Asuka period|ja|飛鳥時代|12=draft}}, the historical Munakata District included the northwestern part of {{ill|Kurate District|ja|鞍手郡|12=draft}} (western {{ill|Miyawaka|ja|宮若市|12=draft}} and {{ill|Kurate|ja|鞍手町|12=draft}}), which formed the ancient broad Munakata region. 

